quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  68,34,"Pellet, hino woodani gom…óu…ìe …ìen ka Joomi ma…ì…ìe, Aljannaaji neema"
  68,35,Kere Men wa…óay jebbilii…ìe …ìen wano bom…ìe …ìen
  68,36,"Ko he…ìi on, si …óon √±aawira non"
  68,37,"Kaa hi…óon mari Deftere, nde janngoton e mun"
  68,38,"Pellet, ko woodani on e mayre, ko ko su…ìoto…óon"
  68,39,"Kaa ko fodooje woodani on e Amen, hoolnii…óe haa √ëalnde Darngal, wonnde pellet, hino woodani on ko √±aawoton kon"
  68,40,Lamndii …ìe ko hommbo e ma…ì…ìe fawtanii…ìe …óum
  68,41,"Kaa ko kafidii…ìe woodani …ìe? Awa yo …ìe addu kafidii…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, si tawii ko …ìe goongu…ìe"
  68,42,"√ëalnde belenru √±oroytee, …ìe noddee e sujjugol kono hara …ìe waawataa. @Corrected"
  68,43,"Hara gite ma…ì…ìe …óen no heli, koyeera no suddi …ìe. Ko tawde …ìe noddeteno e sujjugol fewndo ka …ìe waawunoo"
  68,44,Accidam e kala fennu…óo ndee yewtere; aray nde Men suynira …ìe nokku ka …ìe anndaa
  68,45,"Mi…óo nennan …ìe. Pellet non, pewje Am …óen ko tii…óu…óe"
  68,46,"Kaa a lamndi …ìe njo…ìdi, hara ko yo…ìugol ndi teddani …ìe"
  68,47,"Kaa …ìe anndu fii wirnii…ói …óin, hara hi…ìe winndira […óim hujjaaji ma…ì…ìe]"
  68,48,"Mu√±√±or √±aawoore Joomi maa nden, hara a wa'aali wa wonndii…óo linngii ngii fewndo o noddunoo [Joomi makko] himo sunii"
  68,49,"Si tawno mo∆¥∆¥ere immorde e Joomi makko hewtitanooki mo, ko pellet, o bugeteno e wulaa hara ko o felnii…óo"
  68,50,"Joomi makko su…ìii mo, O wa…ói mo e mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen"
  68,51,"Hay yeddu…ìe …ìen e…ì…ìiinoo yuwirgol ma gite ma…ì…ìe …óen, nde …ìe nanunoo Janntoore nden, hi…ìe wi'a: \"On ko haangaa…óo"
  68,52,"Ndee [Alqur‚Äôaanaare] wonaali, si wanaa waaju tageefo ngon"